SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-10-18 00:33:05.585 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (15ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"
2025-10-18 00:33:05.773 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (82ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e

        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."CreatedAt", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

FROM pg_class AS cls

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                classid=(

2025-10-18 01:30:56.975 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((

) AS t

    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"

) AS t

LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."EmployeeId"), (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."EmployeeId"), (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e3
    WHERE t."Id" = e3."EmployeeId")
FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CompanyId", e."DepartmentId", e."Email", e."EmployeeId", e."EmployeePositionId", e."FirstName", e."LastName", e."Phone", e."ProjectId", e."Status", e."SubDepartmentId"
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    ORDER BY e."EmployeeId"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON t."DepartmentId" = d."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SubDepartments" AS s ON t."SubDepartmentId" = s."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EmployeePositions" AS e0 ON t."EmployeePositionId" = e0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."EmployeeId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 10:35:15.343 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 10:46:43.877 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (31ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

) AS t

    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

2025-10-18 11:05:50.306 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-10-18 11:16:54.752 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (23ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

    ELSE ''

    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

    WHERE EXISTS (

        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."AssetId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row

    ) AS t1

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"

    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."CreatedAt", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        WHERE s."Id" = e."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e0

        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Assets" AS a

2025-10-18 11:33:45.812 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[@__request_AssignedTo_0='?', @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."AssetId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        WHERE a."Id" = e."AssetId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."AssetId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e1 ON e0."EmployeeId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

) AS t

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."AssetId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        WHERE a."Id" = e."AssetId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."AssetId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e1 ON e0."EmployeeId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

) AS t

    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    WHERE s."AssignedTo" = @__request_AssignedTo_0
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t

LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."AssetId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0

        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."AssetId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (

    FROM "Assets" AS a
    WHERE EXISTS (

        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e

    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

        WHERE a."Id" = e."AssetId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."AssetId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e1 ON e0."EmployeeId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Assets" AS a
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
    WHERE a."Id" = e."AssetId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
2025-10-18 12:01:27.397 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__request_AssignedTo_0='?', @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."AssetId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        WHERE a."Id" = e."AssetId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."AssetId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e1 ON e0."EmployeeId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls

WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT e2."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e2."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."CreatedAt", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        WHERE s."Id" = e."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e."EmployeeId" = @__request_AssignedTo_0 AND e."Status" = 1)
    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e1."FirstName", e1."LastName", 1 AS c0, e0."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e0."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e0."Id", e1."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e0

        WHERE e0."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."CreatedAt", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

) AS t

LEFT JOIN "EmployeePositions" AS e0 ON t."EmployeePositionId" = e0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (

    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

2025-10-18 12:26:52.203 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."CreatedAt", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC

    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0

    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e

    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

2025-10-18 12:46:48.205 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e

    ) AS t1

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"

2025-10-18 12:56:17.604 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

2025-10-18 13:04:43.360 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

2025-10-18 13:07:25.295 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (125ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (

) AS t

    LIMIT 1
) AS t

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."PurchaseOrderId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

                objid=cls.oid AND

    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

2025-10-18 18:00:51.360 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (13ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Employees" AS e
2025-10-18 18:00:51.457 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Projects" AS p
2025-10-18 18:00:51.570 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (30ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"

        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

2025-10-18 18:01:09.805 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."Cost", s."ExpiryDate", s."LicenseKey", s."LicenseType", s."PoNumber", s."ProjectId", s."PurchaseDate", s."Seats", s."SoftwareName", s."Status", s."Vendor"
    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
ORDER BY t."ExpiryDate"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 18:05:00.994 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."EmployeeId", t."FirstName", t."LastName", t."Email", t."Phone", d."Name", s."Name", e0."Name", p."Name", c."Name", t."Status", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."EmployeeId"), (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e2
    WHERE t."Id" = e2."EmployeeId"), (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e3
    WHERE t."Id" = e3."EmployeeId")
FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CompanyId", e."DepartmentId", e."Email", e."EmployeeId", e."EmployeePositionId", e."FirstName", e."LastName", e."Phone", e."ProjectId", e."Status", e."SubDepartmentId"
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    ORDER BY e."EmployeeId"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON t."DepartmentId" = d."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SubDepartments" AS s ON t."SubDepartmentId" = s."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EmployeePositions" AS e0 ON t."EmployeePositionId" = e0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."EmployeeId"

2025-10-18 19:01:34.081 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (69ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

2025-10-18 19:01:34.951 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-10-18 19:06:16.493 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (21ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 19:06:37.433 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (22ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 19:06:46.001 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-10-18 19:18:39.831 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (31ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 19:19:06.952 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (16ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-18 19:19:41.345 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"
